				</div>

				<h2 class="h1_title">商家推荐</h2>
				<div class="text_box_2">
					<div class="part_box_2">
						<div class="list-item">
							<img src="https://d3l76hx23vw40a.cloudfront.net/recipe/bk186-024.jpg">
							<strong>黄金炒饭</strong>
						</div>
						<div>
							<p>黄金炒饭以其独特的口味而受到喜爱。经过炒制的米饭会变得松软，颗粒分明，吸收了各种调味料和食材的香味，使其口感丰富而美味。</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="part_box_2">
						<div class="list-item">
							<img src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/n6ZWHlXESHg/maxresdefault.jpg">
							<strong>日式鳗鱼饭</strong>
						</div>
						<div>
							<p>它是将烤鳗鱼切片放在一碗温热的蒸饭上，再淋上特制的鳗鱼酱汁，搭配其他配料而成的一道美味佳肴。</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="part_box_2">
						<div class="list-item">
							<img src="https://imageproxy.icook.network/resize?background=255%2C255%2C255&height=1200&nocrop=false&stripmeta=true&type=auto&url=http%3A%2F%2Ftokyo-kitchen.icook.tw.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fuploads%2Frecipe%2Fcover%2F257355%2F221753fee684baa9.jpg&width=1200">
							<strong>糖醋排骨</strong>
						</div>
						<div>
							<p>它的外观呈现红亮油亮的色泽，肉质鲜嫩多汁，口感糯软，酸甜味道适中，深受人们喜爱。</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="part_box_2">
						<div class="list-item">
							<img src="https://tokyo-kitchen.icook.network/uploads/recipe/cover/382821/6cd3cc27ac64a26f.jpg">
							<strong>传统香鸡排</strong>
						</div>
						<div>
							<p>它的外观金黄酥脆，肉质鲜嫩多汁，带有浓郁的香味，成为了许多人的美食选择。</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="Ads_box_1">
					<img class="Ads_1" src="~/Image/广告1.png">
					<p>甘芳之食报道 @@ wengchin123456@gmail.com</p>
